  <summary>2/27/2003--Introduced.
Military Retiree Dislocation Assistance Act - Authorizes the payment of a primary dislocation allowance for a member of the armed forces who is retired, or placed on a temporary disability retired list, and who actually moves from the member's last duty station to a home selected by the member for purposes of travel and transportation allowances.</summary>
